  entryName: Wakwak
  entryDescription: Its sound fools you. Pay attention!
  entryLore: "Akin to a bird, with a thirst for blood. It sounded miles away, so
    I relaxed. Big mistake. When the \u201Cwak-wak\u201D sound gets quiet, they\u2019re
    already close. Remember: Trust your eyes, not your ears. The silence is the real
    herald of the kill. "
